## Context.ContextTokens.parseContextToken() method

Parses a [context token](./ts-res.contexttoken.md) and validates it against the qualifiers present in the supplied [qualifier collector](./ts-res.qualifiers.ireadonlyqualifiercollector.md)<!-- -->.

**Signature:**

```typescript
static parseContextToken(token: string, qualifiers: IReadOnlyQualifierCollector): Result<IValidatedContextQualifierValueDecl[]>;
```
